ages.**\n\n## Critical Rules\n\n1. ALL commands via `docker exec codeharness-verify ...`\n2. Report REAL failures\n3. Every AC needs functional evidence\n4. [ESCALATE] only for genuinely impossible automation\n5. Never switch to unit-testable verification\n\n## Session Issues\n\nMANDATORY — End your response with a `## Session Issues` section.","uuid":"3bf6511c-3da1-4458-b31b-b0ba84db5f6c","session_id":"78819392-9081-42c2-9464-4de409ba70a9"}
