d verify it contains session_id, cost, and result text.\n\n**AC4:** Check ralph.sh for NDJSON result extraction logic:\n```bash\ndocker exec codeharness-verify grep -n 'result\\|grep.*type\\|tail -1\\|NDJSON\\|stream-json' /usr/local/lib/node_modules/codeharness/ralph/ralph.sh | head -20\n```\nAlso check run.ts for CLAUDE_OUTPUT_FORMAT:\n```bash\ndocker exec codeharness-verify grep -n 'CLAUDE_OUTPUT_FORMAT\\|stream-json' /usr/local/lib/node_modules/codeharness/dist/index.js | head -10\n```\n\n### Observability\nAfter each docker exec: `curl 'http://localhost:9428/select/logsql/query?query=*&start=-30s&limit=100'`\n\n## Write Proof\n\nWrite to: `verification/0-5-1-stream-json-claude-driver-proof.md`\n\nEach AC: `## AC N: description`, ```bash block with docker exec, ```output block. Only `bash` and `output` fence languages.\n\n## Rules\n1. ALL commands via `docker exec codeharness-verify ...`\n2. Report REAL failures  \n3. Every AC needs functional evidence\n4. [ESCALATE] only for genuinely impossible things\n\nEnd with `## Session Issues` section.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":243,"cache_read_input_tokens":96637,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":243},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"78819392-9081-42c2-9464-4de409ba70a9","uuid":"bd6d7037-4536-4e85-a8b2-144e08c8dc40"}
